id: pm-nt1y
title: Dynamic package commands should reject excess args and unknown parent tokens
description: Package audit found descriptor-backed dynamic commands ignoring excess positionals and parent/list aliases accepting unknown child tokens (for example templates show bug extra-token and test-runs nope). Enforce registered command argument metadata at runtime so package authors get safe SDK defaults.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,dogfood-2026-06-12,packages,sdk
created_at: "2026-06-17T22:07:26.015Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-17T23:12:42.115Z"
author: codex-audit-20260618
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: Added descriptor-backed dynamic command validation plus linked-test-adapter arity guards.
expected_result: "Dynamic extension/package commands reject missing required args, extra positionals, and unknown options with agent-actionable usage errors."
actual_result: src/cli/main.ts validates descriptor arity/options; test-runs commands validate run IDs; focused tests/full coverage/dogfood passed.
